name: Style Nebula Magic
description:
Hello! This is my first public Textual Inversion that was trained with DreamArtist.

As the name says, it produces very beautiful nebulas and starry skies along with making different parts of the image sparkly or colorful if a sky isn't present.

Example images were generated with various public models on here, except one that was generated with my own personal mix...but the results should still be beautiful regardless. :)

Some images also utilized lower weights of Torino Aqua Style LoRA

I hope you enjoy it and are able to create beautiful things that bring joy to your life! :)
